<!-- START OF WELCOME SECTION -->
<section id="welcome" class="welcome-container">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to the Dingle Running Festival</h1>
        <p>
            Situated on the spectacular Dingle Peninsula in County Kerry, Ireland, this festival is surely one of the most scenic running festivals of its kind in the world.
            Dingle town comes alive during the festival with an incredible atmosphere and good times guaranteed all weekend. The Dingle Running Festival is not just a running event; it is the experience of a lifetime.
            Many seasoned international runners have described the Dingle Marathon as simply the best that they have experienced in the entire world.
            The unique “Dingle vibe” is very difficult for us to explain but once you’ve experienced it you’ll never forget it!
            There are amazing local sightseeing attractions like ‘Dingle Peninsula’, ‘Dingle Bay’, "Slea Head" and 'Dunmore Head'.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
<!-- END OF WELCOME SECTION -->

<br>

